content.visibleText: public void execute(Database.BatchableContext bc, List<Campaign> campaigns) { System.debug('ComputeCellMetricsBatch processing: ' + campaigns.size() + ' records.'); if (campaigns.size() <= 0) { System.debug('Nothing to process!'); return; } DateTime referenceDateForPerformanceAnalysis = DateTime.now().addDays(-7 * (Integer)LinkedIn_Integration__c.getOrgDefaults()); List<Job_Board_Cell_Analytics__c> analytics = new List<Job_Board_Cell_Analytics__c>(); for (Campaign campaign : campaigns) { Id cellId = campaign.Job_Board_Cell__c; String recruitingCampaignRecordType = DeveloperName; SourcingPlatformDetails platform = SourcingPlatformRepo.getPlatformByName(recruitingCampaignRecordType); if (campaign.Job_Board_Cell__c != null && platform.contains(cellId)) { continue; } processedCells.put(getRecordTypeName().add(cellId)); AggregateResult sumResults = (AggregateResult) [ SELECT MAX(CreatedDate) MostRecentTest, SUM(LsHp__c) MQIs, SUM(EssQ__c) SQIs, SUM(PassengerVolume__c) InterviewerPassers FROM Opportunity WHERE CreatedDate >= referenceDateForPerformanceAnalysis AND Campaign.Job_Board_DeveloperName = platform.recruitingCampaignRecordType AND Campaign.Job_Board_Cell__c = cellId ]; }
